---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="About" description="About FlowHat Blog">
	<h1>About FlowHat Blog</h1>
	<p>
		FlowHat Blog is an independent publication focused on LLMs, agents, coding tools, and practical
		workflows.
	</p>
	<p>
		The goal is simple: publish useful posts that do more than summarize announcements. Each post
		is meant to add evaluation, synthesis, comparisons, or practical guidance that helps someone
		actually use the tools.
	</p>
	<p>
		The scope is intentionally narrow for now: models, agent products, coding agents, subagents,
		multimodal workflows, and the operational details around using them well.
	</p>
	<p>
		This site may include analytics, marketplace links, and future advertising placements as the
		publication grows. When that happens, disclosure information will be kept visible on the site.
	</p>
</PageLayout>
